snippet.title: Space Impact on Nokia 3310
snippet.description:
All levels from this great game. It was really uncomfortable to record it, so please excuse it's quality.

Level 1: 0:03
Level 2: 1:27
Level 3: 2:37
Level 4: 3:52
Level 5: 5:15
Level 6: 6:56
Level 7: 8:30
Level 8: 9:37


There's no sound in ths video, that was intentional. I might record a new, better one, with sounds... eventually.... some day...


The phone actually is Nokia 3310, just with 3330 front cover. I think the phone looks gorgeous like that.

For PC remake visit https://sipc.lukew.cz
